timeline_events.description: A bearded player takes a powerful, first-time shot with his right foot, hitting the back-left of the net.
A player in a white shirt shoots with their right foot from just outside the penalty area into the top right corner.
A player in a white shirt shoots from distance, and the ball goes low into the bottom left corner of the goal.
A powerful shot hits the top bar of the goal and deflects down into the net for a goal.
A powerful shot from a player in a white shirt hits the inside of the left goalpost and deflects into the net.
An orange bibs player intercepts a pass and scores with a low shot into the bottom left corner.
A powerful shot from a player in a black shirt hits the inside of the left goalpost and goes in.
Following a saved shot, a player in a reddish/pink t-shirt scores on the rebound from a tight angle.
An orange bibs player scores with a long-range shot from just behind the center line into the top left corner.
A player takes a shot from just outside the center circle that goes into the bottom left of the goal.
A shot hits the inside of the left goalpost and deflects into the net.
A player in a white shirt shoots from the left, scoring in the bottom left corner of the goal.
A player in blue trousers takes a powerful, low shot with his left foot into the bottom corner of the net.
A player in a black shirt receives a pass and shoots the ball into the top right corner of the net.
A shot hits the underside of the crossbar and bounces down over the goal line.
A player in blue shorts shoots from the left side, and the ball hits the goal frame and goes into the net.
A player takes a long-range shot from just outside the center circle into the top left corner.
A player shoots from near the center circle line, and the ball goes into the bottom left of the net.
After a kick-off, a player in a dark top takes a right-footed shot that goes low into the bottom left corner.
A player shoots from just outside the center circle, scoring in the bottom left corner of the net.

match_summary: This was a one-sided match where the no bibs/colours team demonstrated superior finishing and attacking pressure, scoring consistently throughout the game. The orange bibs team scored a few notable long-range goals but were ultimately unable to keep pace with the relentless scoring from their opponents.
